cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR 

The paper deals with object detection in road scenes using deep learning and polarimetric imaging. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves autonomous vehicles and driving assistance systems, which falls under the category of cs.RO (Robotics). The use of deep neural networks for object detection suggests the category of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also involves the use of machine learning algorithms, which falls under the category of cs.LG (Machine Learning). Finally, the paper involves image processing and analysis, which falls under the category of cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
